&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the end-to-end movement of benefit funds through Maven&#39;s payments infrastructure, ensuring transaction accuracy, timely disbursement, and integrity across the full funding pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own client invoicing for benefit funding programs and the timely reconciliation of complex claims bank account transactions and balances to ensure high-integrity financial operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor clinic and provider payments against contracted timeliness standards, identify systemic delays or SLA gaps, and partner with operations to resolve root causes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage Maven&#39;s floated benefit funding program, including tracking outstanding float balances, driving timely recoupment from clients, and escalating aging exposure to Finance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead cross-functional root cause analyses on financial discrepancies to implement structural solutions that prevent billing errors and optimize cash flow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and implement continuous process improvements to increase the efficiency, accuracy, and scalability of the benefit funding funct

